.firstSection {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: calc(100vh);
    /* height: calc(100vh - 0px); */
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-top: 5%;
    /* background-color: aqua; */
}
.firstSection_block {
    position: relative;
    top: 5%;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex-wrap: nowrap;
} 
.firstSection_block_geotec {
    font-family: 'Raleway-Regular';
    font-style: normal;
    color: #4A6AD0;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 47px;
    line-height: 138%;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    width: 863px;
}

.element-animation {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-size: 3rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(80px);
}
  
.element-animation.element-show {
    opacity: 1;
    transition: all 1.5s;
    transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0,.65,.7,1);
    transform: translateY(0%);
}
.element-animation:nth-child(1).element-show {
    transition-delay: 0.1s;
}


.firstSection_block_geotec svg {
    padding: 0px 15px;
    position: relative;
    bottom: 0;
    height: 100%;
}

.firstSection_block_geotec_perhapse_block {
    position: relative;
    height: auto;
    width: auto;
    transition-delay: 0.4s !important;
}
.firstSection_block_geotec_perhapse {
    position: relative;
    margin-top: 83px;
    font-family: 'Raleway-Light';
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #102876;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 26px;
    width: 79%;
}
.top_sec {
    margin-top: 33px;
}
.engFont {
    font-family: 'Poppins-ExtraLight';
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 275;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 26px;
    color: #102876;
}
.bigFontSize {
    font-size: 64px;
    color: #4A6AD0;
    font-family: 'Poppins-ExtraLight';
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 275;
    line-height: 138%;
}

.firstSection_block_geotec_perhapse_width {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    position: relative;
}
.blockCont_block {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;
    padding-right: 85px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    transition-delay: 0.4s !important;
}
.firstSection_block_geotec_block {
    position: relative;
    height: auto;
    width: 57%;
    margin-left: 82px;
}
.blockCont {
    position: relative;
    width: 262px;
    height: 208px;
    background: #4A6AD0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: 0.5s ease-out;
}
.centerer:first-of-type {
    margin-right: 77px;
}
.blockCont img {
    padding-top: 29px;
    padding-left: 31px;
    transition: 0.5s ease-out;
}
.blockCont .svgcustomers {
    padding-top: 29px;
    padding-left: 31px;
    transition: 0.5s ease-out;
}
.svgcustomers g rect {
    fill: #FFFFFF;
    transition: 0.5s ease-out;
}
.blockCont_text {
    font-family: 'Raleway-Light';
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 26px;
    text-transform: capitalize;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    padding-top: 12px;
    padding-left: 28px;
    transition: 0.5s ease-out;
}
.blockCont .svgLine {
    position: absolute;
    right: 31px;
    bottom: 28px;
    transition: 0.5s ease-out;
}
.blockCont .svgLine path {
    fill: #FFFFFF;
    transition: 0.5s ease-out;
} 


.centerer {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease-out;
    transition-delay: cubic-bezier(.13,.65,.24,.95);
  }
  .centerer:hover {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }
  .centerer:hover .svgLine {
    transform: scale(0.97);
  }
  .centerer:hover .svgcustomers {
    transform: scale(0.97);
  }
  .centerer:hover .svgcustomers g rect {
    fill: #4a69d0;
  }
  .centerer:hover .blockCont {
    background: #4a69d000;
    border: 1px solid #4a69d065;
  }
  .centerer:hover .blockCont_text {
    color: #4a69d0;
  }
  .centerer:hover .blockCont .svgLine path {
    fill: #4a69d0;
  }
  
  [class^=btn-] {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    /* width: 210px;
    height: 60px; */
    text-transform: uppercase;
    /* border: 1px solid currentColor; */
  }
  
  .btn-6 {
    overflow: hidden;
    /* color: #31b462; */
  }
  .btn-6 span {
    position: absolute;
    display: block;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #dadadaaf;
    transition: width 0.4s ease-in-out, height 0.4s ease-in-out;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    z-index: 9999;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }
  .btn-6:hover {
    color: #c3e9d1;
  }
  .btn-6:hover span {
    width: 255%;
    height: 592.5px;
  }
